<p>Content distribution separates the blogs that grow from the blogs that stall. The content itself is only half the equation. How you distribute it determines whether anyone reads it.</p>
<p>Pick 2-3 channels. Build a repeatable system. Measure everything. The businesses that win are not the ones creating the most content. They are the ones distributing it best.</p>
